channel.title: Looking to exchange usenet invite for private tracker invite
channel.description:
I have a nzbs.in invite, I'm looking to trade it for access to a private torrent tracker so I can get some missing TV shows using my dedi as a seedbox.
Tracker needs to be decent for HD TV releases and older less common TV rips etc if possible, not interested in the music ones, sorry.
